ielders]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Bogot\u00e1]]\n\n\n{{Colombia-footy-midfielder-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name             = Juli\u00e1n Guillermo\n| image                  = \n| fullname               = Julian Guillermo Rojas\n| birth_date            = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1990|2|28}}\n| birth_place = [[Bogot\u00e1]], [[Colombia]]\n| currentclub            = [[Independiente Santa Fe]]\n| clubnumber         = 8\n| height                 = {{height|m=1.76|precision=0}}\n| position               = [[Midfielder]]\n| years1 = 2007\u20132008 \n| years2 = 2008\u20132009  \n| years3 = 2010\u20132012\n| years4 = 2012\u20132013\n| years5 = 2013\u2013present\n| clubs1 = [[Academia F.C.|Academia]]\n| clubs2 = [[C\u00facuta Deportivo]] \n| clubs3 = [[Club Atletico Banfield|Banfield]]\n| clubs4 = [[Independiente Medell\u00edn]]\n| clubs5 = [[Independiente Santa Fe]]\n| caps1 =                \n| caps2 =    \n| caps3 =   \n| caps4 =  \n| goals1 =    \n| goals2 =   \n| goals3 =   \n| goals4 =     \n| pcupdate               = \n| ntupdate               = June 8, 2012\n}}\n\n'''Julian Guillermo Rojas''' (born February 28, 1990 in [[Bogot\u00e1, Colombia]]) is a Colombian [[association football|footballer]] currently playing for [[Club Independiente Santa Fe]] of the [[Categor\u00eda Primera A|Colombian First Division]].\n\n==References==\n* [http://www.bdfa.com.ar/jugadores-JULIAN-GUILLERMO-54278.html Profile at BDFA] {{in lang|es}}\n* {{Soccerway|julian-guillermo-rojas/132912}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Guillermo, Julian}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Colombian footballers]]\n[[Category:Academia F.C. players]]\n[[Category:C\u00facuta Deportivo footballers]]\n[[Category:Banfield footballers]]\n[[Category:Independiente Medell\u00edn footballers]]\n[[Category:Independiente Santa Fe footballers]]\n[[Category:Colombian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Argentina]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Bogot\u00e1]]\n\n\n{{Colombia-footy-midfielder-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Colombian footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juli%C3%A1n_Guillermo"}
